{"tid":1473763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[今日兩點] 第 四 次 民 間 記 者 會 集 氣 加 油 區","createTime":"2019-08-15T02:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:26:08.000Z","uid":74888,"like":159,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"94cd080b65666eab80a9a4a2a2236112c8606380","tid":1473763,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"第四次的民間記者會主題為：「 官警黑亂港禍經濟    」。 團隊希望能借是次機會，提供多角度意見， 還原事實真 相    ，從而反駁警方及政府過去的謊言、以及社會的誤解和迷思。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg4aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=1de6d7bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/citizenspresscon</a><br />\n<br />\n希望今次個講稿可以有多D數據支持論點<br />\n答問題果陣時唔洗緊張慢慢諗左先答!!!! <br />\n巴打絲打們加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3053f39377b15f21ff7ea45582c25a3c74ad167","tid":1473763,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"加油！！！！"},{"pid":"3adb337e4b082da933e657fbf0eef6886ebbe18b","tid":1473763,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:58:34.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"c89e4c6ec043949d70d4f1da5b094dd75f6fe260","tid":1473763,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3a5cd745e015cc83134709f862a67b85a64