b","tid":1473763,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵<br />\n林鄭月娥忍心將香港推進粉身碎骨深淵<br />\n記者請日日問<br />\n</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"30668318de188b6168b6898c8da348743fa6c838","tid":1473763,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 香港警方=黑社會=恐怖主義組織</span></span></div><br />\n811--黑 警假扮示威者掟磚同火魔法<br />\n811--尖沙咀 6名警察扮示威者 帶隊召黑衫人 帶頭燒警署<br />\n811--銅鑼灣 警察扮示威者射丫叉 混入人群搞事後表露身分制服旁人同時大量防暴增援<br />\n811--以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n811--北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 黑警假扮示威者掟磚同火魔法<br />\n香港警察濫用暴力及喬裝成示威者煽動並參與暴力<br />\n記者請日日問</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"25f8d2f49ded28166c8155ffe2dc8c27451b13f3","tid":1473763,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:40:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲 </span></span></div><br />\n黑社會無差別襲擊人，警方唔拉黑社會<br />\n警黑合作， 警署落閘， 999唔通，無人被檢控 <br />\n721元朗恐襲第26日: 無人被檢控， 無警停職， 施襲者逍遙法外，市民安全零保障<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵!<br />\n </div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 香港警方=黑社會， 香港警方=恐怖主義組織<br />\n香港人一世都唔原諒香港警察<br />\n無忘721<br />\n記者請日日問</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"f180cdcfaa4dbc1576228edde010020280b638d1","tid":1473763,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:41:52.000Z","msg":"加油呀"},{"pid":"e2a6c7772511516e160be5346a0ed3986ec1b158","tid":1473763,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ddca20ea81de4d4233112f35db6cf97d1a190a5b","tid":1473763,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:42:33.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />民記係奇蹟黎"},{"pid":"8b71273859dc41e22cbb95e708d8e318ec7926e4","tid":1473763,"uid":4001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"aa14a70d0d5358c13df80614dd72c331d6f9398b","tid":1473763,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"對住大公/文匯果d記者問題，諗多陣，商量下先好答呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持！"},{"pid":"362e201fb0d4decf88ec73cf93de14e65193407f","tid":1473763,"uid":103353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"各位加油"},{"pid":"d9b37ebba388d9579eb9271777cca28009c4f081","tid":1473763,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:09:32.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"8e4cbd5486498695e04270a4d835b288a74dcb17","tid":1473763,"uid":196117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:09:45.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"7c7459900f403a764075570f8554d285136ab004","tid":1473763,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04679ca7b571b02552161778778e00e759376a47","tid":1473763,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6d3ca360acf1cfba3306acfda4116a2ebf8b43f","tid":1473763,"uid":121409,"like":0,"disl